# Pallindrome --> If a word read from first and last is same then it is called pallindrome

a = input("Enter Word : ")
rev_a = a[::-1]
if a == rev_a:
    print(f"It is a Pallidrome : {a}")
else:
    print(f"It is not a Pallindrome : {a}")
    
    
    
Enter Word : madam
It is a Pallidrome : madam
